<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 30 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items from the
Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong Sunday:

hke053001 -- Uzbek FM to Visit Pakistan from Monday
hke053002 -- 97 Fire Cases Reported in Myanmar in April
