<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 31 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major world
cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on June 1, issued by China's
Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
