<HEADLINE> 1994 Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, May 31 (Xinhua) -- South Africa's second
democratic general election will be held on Wednesday, June 2.
Following are the results of the first all-race democratic
election in 1994:
</P>
<P>
Name of Party  % of votes Seats in National Assembly
</P>
<P>
ANC  63.0  252
</P>
<P>
NP  20.5 82
</P>
<P>
