enactment of laws banning smoking in public places along with
resisting pro-smoking campaigns in the mass media.
</P>
<P>
"Smoking is a potential public health threat and a large number
of smokers pollute the environment every day," he said while
speaking at a discussion here, which was organized by MANOSH, an
anti-drug association, on the occasion of "World No Tobacco Day".
</P>
<P>
