in Hubei Province and said that people will never forget their
contributions to the successful battle against flooding. He
pointed out that to continue to increase the nation's economic
power provides the foundation for resolving all types of social
issues, including the modernization of defense and the armed
forces.
</P>
<P>
China must simultaneously increase its economic power and
continuously increase defense capability, said Jiang.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese president repeatedly emphasized the importance of
correctly handling the relationships between reform, development
and stability.  
