Norman Mailer said that NATO's war against Yugoslavia has turned
into obscenity with its strategy of restricting military action to
bombing so that the blood of NATO troops will not be shed. Mailer
also warned that NATO's manipulation of national and international
public opinion and emotion could well lead to catastrophe.
</P>
