failed to achieve its goals, said Korapierinykof, adding that the
bombing of the Chinese Embassy in Belgrade not only caused serious
casualties and property losses, but also constituted a gross
provocation against Chinese people and a wanton trampling on the
norms governing international relations.
</P>
<P>
He added that Russia will enhance coordination and cooperation
with China in order to promote friendly and cooperative military
relations within the framework of the cooperative Russia-China
strategic partnership and contribute to maintaining peace in the
region and the world at large. 
